subject: Ice Dancing
Awards, Decorations and Honors
Olympic Games (2010)
lead_paragraph: Meryl Davis and Charlie White won their second ice dancing national title by defeating the Olympic medalists Tanith Belbin and Ben Agosto for the first time.
